---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="Privacy Policy">
    <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-24">
        <header class="mb-20">
            <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-thin tracking-[0.4em] uppercase text-white mb-6 text-center">
                Privacy <span class="text-gold italic">Policy</span>
            </h1>
            <div class="h-px w-24 bg-gold/30 mx-auto"></div>
        </header>

        <div class="space-y-16 text-gray-400 font-light leading-relaxed text-sm md:text-base tracking-wide">
            
            <section class="border-l border-gold/20 pl-6 lg:pl-10">
                <h2 class="text-white uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-4 text-sm font-medium">1. Data Controller</h2>
                <p>
                    Utopia Studio (Operating as [Insert Your Official SRL Name Here]) acts as the data controller for any personal information you provide. We are committed to protecting your privacy in accordance with GDPR regulations.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="border-l border-gold/20 pl-6 lg:pl-10">
                <h2 class="text-white uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-4 text-sm font-medium">2. Data Collection & Use</h2>
                <p>
                    When you use our request forms, we collect your <strong>name, surname, email address, and phone number</strong>. This information is used exclusively to contact you regarding your inquiry, manage your bookings, and provide the services requested.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="border-l border-gold/20 pl-6 lg:pl-10">
                <h2 class="text-white uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-4 text-sm font-medium">3. Payments & Financial Security</h2>
                <p>
                    All financial transactions are processed through <strong>Stripe secure checkout links</strong>. Utopia Studio does not collect, see, or store your credit card or bank account details. Your payment information is provided directly to Stripe, whose use of your personal information is governed by their own Privacy Policy.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="border-l border-gold/20 pl-6 lg:pl-10">
                <h2 class="text-white uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-4 text-sm font-medium">4. Data Retention</h2>
                <p>
                    Your contact information is stored only for as long as necessary to fulfill the purposes for which it was collected, including for the purposes of satisfying any legal or accounting requirements.
                </p>
            </section>

            <section class="border-l border-gold/20 pl-6 lg:pl-10">
                <h2 class="text-white uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-4 text-sm font-medium">5. Your Rights</h2>
                <p>
                    Under GDPR, you have the right to access, correct, or request the deletion of your personal data. To exercise these rights or for any questions regarding your data, please contact us via Instagram <span class="text-gold italic">@utopia.artstudio</span> or via our official contact channels.
                </p>
            </section>

            <div class="pt-20 text-center">
                <p class="text-[10px] text-gray-600 uppercase tracking-[0.5em]">Last Updated: February 2026</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-24 text-center">
            <a href="/home" class="inline-block bg-[#0F393D] text-white px-10 py-3 rounded-full font-light italic text-[10px] tracking-[0.3em] transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-white hover:text-[#0F393D] hover:shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(255,255,255,0.2)]">
                Return to Studio
            </a>
        </div>
    </main>
</MainLayout>